<a href="http://hhsw.de/sites/Soyuz404/" class="ScreenshotLink"><img src="screenshots/soyuz404.jpg" alt="Soyuz 404 Screenshot"/></a>
<p>A space adventure in 13 kilobytes.</p>
<p>Works on your phone, too. Keep the finger on the screen to explore a scene. Lifting the finger over something does use that something.</p>
