<article><a name="jumpy_green"><h2>Jumpy Green</h2></a>
<a href="http://jumpygreen.markusfisch.de" class="ScreenshotLink"><img src="screenshots/jumpy_green.jpg" alt="Jumpy Green Screenshot"/></a>
<p>A little green man trying to get evil astronauts off his small world.</p>
<p>Get rid of Buck Rodgers by jumping high when he's on the opposite side of the world. If jump high enough, he'll be thrown off your world and get lost in space again.</p>
